727262f-c.text:
Little Neck Parkway, west side, near 74th Avenue, showing the Henry Cox (Cocks) house of 1873-1891. lIn 1891 the farm contained 104 acres and stretched north from Motor Parkway from where views 2 and 3 were taken. View 1: Eugene L. Armbruster Collection 1922
Views, 2,3r P.L. Sperr
NO REIRODCTIONS  March 1, 1927
